036a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tHe believes anywhere between 20 to 25 cars could be built. Pricing wasn&#8217;t mentioned but Skytop would certainly command a massive premium over the 8 Series Convertible donor car, priced at $100,500. Since the concept had the most powerful V-8 ever used by BMW, it was likely based on the M8 Convertible, available from $148,800.\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-abe1e80 e-con-full quote-single e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"abe1e80\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-92cb624 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"92cb624\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Pellentesque dui dui, laoreet eget libero quis, maximus cursus metus. Integer id nibh sit amet purus congue mollis. \u201d\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-516b4ed elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"516b4ed\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsaid Mike Fratantoni, MBA\u2019s chief economist.\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-788bc3e e-grid e-con-full e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"788bc3e\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ad5d1b2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"ad5d1b2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"